            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">328 Mickle Street</name>
                    <name type="place">Camden New Jersey<ptr target="loc.01150_n1"/></name> 
                    <date when="1884-03-27" rend="right">March 27</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>

            <p>&#8212;I am getting well towards my usual (late year) state of health<!--<ptr target="n0129"
                />-->&#8212;have had a bad time ever since I saw you in Phila<ptr target="loc.01150_n2"
                />&#8212;my own illness, confinement to the house (a chilly, stagnant lonesome three
                weeks)&#8212;sudden sickness &#38; death, (hasty consumption) of a young fellow I
                was much attached to, a near neighbor, &#38; now the flitting&#8212;I moved
                yesterday (above address) &#38; shall remain here for the present<ptr
                    target="loc.01150_n3"/>&#8212;it is half way nearer the
                ferry&#8212;write&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>W W</signed>
            </closer>

        </body>
